{"id":605165,"title":"28｜常见的内置数据类型都何时使用？","content":"<p><strong>课后习题</strong><br>\n请根据本讲学习的数据类型，回答以下问题。</p><ol>\n<li>当你需要存储不重复的数据时，可以采用哪种数据类型？</li>\n<li>当你既需要存储数字，又要存储字符时，可以采用那种数据类型？</li>\n<li>当你需要存储汉字时，可以采用哪种数据类型？</li>\n</ol><p><strong>课程代码、课件及其他相关资料地址</strong><br>\n<a href=\"https://gitee.com/wilsonyin/zero-basics-python\">https://gitee.com/wilsonyin/zero-basics-python</a></p>","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":363451,"user_name":"Matthew","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":2843865,"ip_address":"江苏","ucode":"96093089773740","user_header":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/PiajxSqBRaEKSVuNarJuDhBSvHY0giaq6yriceEBKiaKuc04wCYWOuso50noqDexaPJJibJN7PHwvcQppnzsDia1icZkw/132","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1669697784,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100310001,"comment_content":"1、当你需要存储不重复的数据时，可以采用哪种数据类型？\n——集合\n\n2、当你既需要存储数字，又要存储字符时，可以采用那种数据类型？\n——列表、元组、集合、字典\n\n3、当你需要存储汉字时，可以采用哪种数据类型？\n——列表、元组、集合、字典","like_count":4},{"had_liked":false,"id":379450,"user_name":"好困啊","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":2094450,"ip_address":"上海","ucode":"D49429660F2DC8","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1f/f5/72/8cbc5cb3.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1691983782,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100310001,"comment_content":"1. 当你需要存储不重复的数据时，可以采用的数据类型是 **集合** (`set`)。集合是一个无序的，不重复的元素集。\n\n2. 当你既需要存储数字，又要存储字符时，你可以采用 **列表** (`list`) 或 **元组** (`tuple`)。这两种数据类型都可以存储不同类型的数据，包括数字、字符串、其他数据结构等。\n\n3. 当你需要存储汉字时，可以采用 **字符串** (`str`) 数据类型。在Python 3.x中，字符串是以Unicode格式存储的，所以可以直接存储汉字。例如：`s = &quot;你好&quot;`。","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":384697,"user_name":"Geek_1e9b5c","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":3786954,"ip_address":"广东","ucode":"C634A7C49DFE9B","user_header":"","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1701345969,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"pro